        public TechnologyTagModel addTagToFileModel(FileModel fileModel,
                                            String tagName,
                                            TechnologyTagLevel level)
        Adds the provided tag to the provided FileModel. If a TechnologyTagModel cannot be found with the provided name, then one will be created.

      • removeTagFromFileModel

        public void removeTagFromFileModel(FileModel fileModel,
                                   String tagName)
        Removes the provided tag from the provided FileModel. If a TechnologyTagModel cannot be found with the provided name, then this operation will do nothing.
